headline: From Pandemic Hobby To 7-Figure Roblox Fashion Empire: How Topcat Sells Over 1 Million Items A Month
summary: Philipp Batura did not originally plan to build a fashion company when he joined Roblox (NYSE:RBLX) in 2020 during the pandemic, but his three-person startup Topcat has grown into one of the platform's largest digital clothing creators, selling more than 1 million items in July alone, according to Forbes.
